{"type": "article", "id": 25072, "title": "带54盏LED灯的吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-07T07:10:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140255nYUH8l0NpejfrFJR.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本设计师 Arihiro Miyake 为丹麦品牌 Moooi 设计的吊灯，使用非常细的金属框架和 54 盏 LED 灯泡，搭建出 3 层环形灯，相互错落又显得很有规律，远看就像是三圈蜡烛。每一盏 LED 灯都有两根金属丝牵引指向中心的轴，分别是正负两极，这些线条穿插本身也形成了精细的感受。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140252RkIzMsNA41J6vLg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140253CrVMsFqevfadmgTo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140253cXezA9OKmb0s7CRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140254cUbD582wVECsrGgO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140254q0hyMufwNt9dEQT8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}